dia brand name. The company offers its services under the CarWale, Shriram Automall, Adroit Auto, BikeWale, CarTrade, DriveASmile, Cartrade Infotech, CarTrade Ventures, Mobility Outlook, and CarWale abSure brands. CarTrade Tech Limited was incorporated in 2000 and is based in Navi Mumbai, India."}}